                      (asm/src/RRDX2.ASM):00650         
4A78 39               (asm/src/RRDX2.ASM):00651                RTS                   RETURN, MY ASS!
                      (asm/src/RRDX2.ASM):00652         *
                      (asm/src/RRDX2.ASM):00653         *UPDATE YOUR DIAGONALS
                      (asm/src/RRDX2.ASM):00654         *
