4A81 BD4954           (asm/src/RRDX2.ASM):00658          JSR WRITE
4A84 10AEA4           (asm/src/RRDX2.ASM):00659          LDY ,Y
4A87 26F5             (asm/src/RRDX2.ASM):00660          BNE DXUPDL
